# ================================================================================
# WHAT THIS FILE IS:
# Tells Git which files and folders to ignore (not track in version control).
#
# WHY YOU NEED IT:
# - Prevents sensitive data (API keys, secrets) from being committed
# - Keeps your repo clean from build artifacts and cache files
# - Avoids committing large files that shouldn't be in version control
# - Essential for security and professionalism
#
# WHAT TO PUT IN IT:
# This template covers Python/AI projects. Add or remove patterns as needed.
# ================================================================================

